title: CryptoKeyType
description:
CryptoKeyType is an XDR Enum defines as:

```text enum CryptoKeyType { KEY_TYPE_ED25519 = 0, KEY_TYPE_PRE_AUTH_TX = 1, KEY_TYPE_HASH_X = 2, KEY_TYPE_ED25519_SIGNED_PAYLOAD = 3, // MUXED enum values for supported type are derived from the enum values // above by ORing them with 0x100 KEY_TYPE_MUXED_ED25519 = 0x100 }; ```
